# Retail Pricing Strategies

## Project Overview
This project focuses on developing and analyzing **Retail Pricing Strategies**. The objective is to explore how pricing affects sales, identify optimal price points, and provide data-driven recommendations to maximize revenue and profitability for retail businesses. By leveraging machine learning techniques such as Linear Regression, we aim to uncover meaningful insights into customer behavior and price sensitivity.

